arts.ttl: Euro 2025: Netherlands sparked by Miedema's 100th goal beats Wales
arts.sum: Netherlands great Vivianne Miedema’s 100th goal in international soccer has been key to a 3-0 win over debut-making Wales at the Women’s European Championship in Lucerne.

arts.ttl: Wales Women v Netherlands Live: Updates as hundreds of fans gather ahead of Euro 2025 match
arts.sum: Almost 4,000 Welsh football fans are set to fill Allmend Stadion in Lucerne.
